page.title: 11CUBS AND BROWNIES
page.content:
{43rd Crosland Moor Cubs}meet on Wednesday. There are 11 cubs, aged 8-11, 2 leaders & 3 helpers. We play Horse and Jockey, Crab Football, Football, The 'fish came out of the sea', Kims game & other games. We go tracking & camping twice a year. The cub hut is on{Moorside Ave.}
The{82nd Brownies}meet at 6.30 at{ {St.Barnabas}church hall, we have to wear a Brownie dress, belt, a purse, a yellow tie, a Brownie hat & brown shoes. We have 2 pack leaders & 14 Brownies. Altogether we have 4 groups: Gnomes, Imps, Pixies, Elves. You have to be 9 or 10 before you can join the Guides. This year the Guides are celebrating 75 yrs. of Guiding.
